snippet.title: POPGOES Arcade 2020 Edition RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD AND PLAY: https://gamejolt.com/games/pa2020/478668

POPGOES Arcade 2020 Edition (PA2020) is a complete reboot of the original POPGOES Arcade game that was released in April 2016. It is a prologue for the upcoming reboot of the original, main POPGOES game.
